high_descs: Turn left to go to the end of the counter on the left.
Pick up the tea kettle in next to the toaster.
Turn right and go to the sink on the other side of the kitchen.
Wash the tea kettle in the sink with running water and pick it up.
Turn around to go to the cabinet on the left of the stove.
Place the tea kettle in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed tea kettle in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the trash can to the right and to the left of the counter
Pick up the kettle from the counter
Turn around and go to the sink
Place the kettle in the sink, turn the water on, fill the sink with water, turn the water off
Pick up the kettle from in the sink and turn around towards the stove
Open the cabinet, put the kettle inside to the left of the stove and close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Placing a kettle in the cabinet
